sequenceDiagram
    participant DS as Data Science
    participant CI as Automated Validation (CI)
    participant ACT as Actuarial
    participant ENG as Engineering
    participant LEG as Legal/Compliance
    participant REG as State Regulator
    participant PROD as Production

    DS->>CI: Commit feature definition + model (PR)
    CI-->>DS: Auto data-quality + back-test results (minutes, not weeks)
    CI->>ACT: Auto-generated rate impact dashboard
    ACT-->>DS: Review comments as PR review (parallel, threaded)
    ACT->>ENG: Approval merges the PR (no re-implementation needed)
    ENG->>LEG: Auto-generated disclosure language for review
    par Filing prep runs in parallel with deployment prep
        LEG->>REG: Submit filing package (auto-populated exhibit)
        ENG->>PROD: Deploy to containerized shadow environment
    end
    REG-->>LEG: Filing approved / effective date confirmed
    ENG->>PROD: Feature-flagged rollout 1% -> 10% -> 100%
    PROD-->>DS: Automated guardrail monitoring + rollback triggers
